  "detailed_description": "In this game you are a test subject that has just been caught by the government. Everything is taken away from you and you must fight the elites to get it back. Sail the seas, drive through mountains, fly in the sky, and break into top-secret labs to beat the the Phy-Op. Through multiple different dimensions and biomes you fight for your freedom back. There is also a multiplayer mode included where you can race other players in karts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles combat and strategy.</h2><br>To gain your power and freedom back, you must learn to use different vehicles to drive and fly through intense boss fights, complex mazes, puzzles and more. The vehicles included are sports cars, planes, submarines, boats and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense First Person Combat</h2>There are multiple levels and biomes where strategic first person combat is needed to defeat your enemies. This includes different weapons and special abilities. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer - Phsy-Op: Karting</h2>Phsy-Opp Karting allows you and up to 8 other players to compete in a kart racing game based on the characters from the story mode. Collect utilities to sabotage your opponents and to bring yourself ahead. This includes 2 maps and more to come!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In this game you are a test subject that has just been caught by the government. Everything is taken away from you and you must fight the elites to get it back. Sail the seas, drive through mountains, fly in the sky, and break into top-secret labs to beat the the Phy-Op. Through multiple different dimensions and biomes you fight for your freedom back. There is also a multiplayer mode included where you can race other players in karts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles combat and strategy.</h2><br>To gain your power and freedom back, you must learn to use different vehicles to drive and fly through intense boss fights, complex mazes, puzzles and more. The vehicles included are sports cars, planes, submarines, boats and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/c0a419dc8cb3832169a25b0b2f6a3cb2.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense First Person Combat</h2>There are multiple levels and biomes where strategic first person combat is needed to defeat your enemies. This includes different weapons and special abilities. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/6190c2dd29eb22081bfca83b6bf87c0a.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer - Phsy-Op: Karting</h2>Phsy-Opp Karting allows you and up to 8 other players to compete in a kart racing game based on the characters from the story mode. Collect utilities to sabotage your opponents and to bring yourself ahead. This includes 2 maps and more to come!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.poster.avif?t=1748548054\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.webm?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716380/extras/f033a84a9b3b65509fe95715a1028ee6.mp4?t=1748548054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
